nodes.text: Level 2685 was a level on Coruscant, in that planet's seedy undercity. Three years after his election to the post of Supreme Chancellor of the Galactic Republic, Sheev Palpatine brought Anakin Skywalker, then a Padawan to Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi, to Club Kasakar, an establishment situated within Level 2685.
